[spazio][spazio][spazio][spazio]Church of Glabados in Mullonde and the

Church's lost influence. His ultimate goal is for the Church
to become the supreme power in Ivalice-greater even
than the Crown itself.

Larg and Goltanna, the High Confessor is using his
Knights Templar to search for the Zodiac Stones in hopes
of winning over the common people.{END}
